name: Angry Bot
description:
The growth of technology makes
humans do all kinds of things easily
and quickly. All aspects of life today
are represented by technology called
robots. When robots have begun to
master almost all aspects of human
life, we want to be vigilant because
excessive and unwise use of
technology might damage our own
lives and environment. Then don't let
us get angry the Bot and they will
destroy our world. Just don't let the
Bot angry.
